      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its mechanical integrity. This chassis features the high-revving S54 inline-six, benefiting from a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rod bearing replacement using VAC coated shells. The rear subframe has been structurally reinforced with precision-welded plates, addressing the platform's primary weak point. Engagement is handled by a short-throw 6-speed Getrag manual transmission feeding a factory limited-slip differential. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint correction required. A turn-key example for the discerning purist.",
