      "description": "Presenting an absolute time-capsule of a vehicle that defies its age. This car is in showroom condition, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and shielded from the elements since new. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks, complemented by pristine alloy wheels wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber. Inside, the cabin is a masterclass in preservation; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing no bolster wear or creasing, and the original factory scent is still present. Every electronic component, switch, and dial operates with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless, backed by a folder of exhaustive service records and an engine bay that is spotlessly clean. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen that looks and drives exactly as it did on the delivery floor. Serious inquiries only; professional inspections are welcomed to verify this vehicle's extraordinary state.",
